{"title":"Image_Classfication","uid":"d0833af25ffe4b7c183344dd301cd999","slug":"Image_Classfication","date":"2021-04-25T06:40:04.949Z","updated":"2021-05-13T15:35:38.416Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Image_Classfication.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h2 id=\"1-AlexNet\"><a href=\"#1-AlexNet\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1 AlexNet\"></a>1 AlexNet</h2><p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/5ET4ZDv1JqIS8lL.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/vyzJbiCAL71Ha92.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"2-VGG\"><a href=\"#2-VGG\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2 VGG\"></a>2 VGG</h2><p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/en3AWpmIDN6lCB2.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/db3mTQrMlU7oc6a.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/dLSYfeqGiZ7snHB.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"3-GooleNet\"><a href=\"#3-GooleNet\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3 GooleNet\"></a>3 GooleNet</h2><p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/LnQVcsykBwO6lE4.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/EV1CzwPiZe7Rfdb.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/1WzMJXECuVdDlQ2.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/CWge7hSu1xGoDsZ.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"4-RestNet\"><a href=\"#4-RestNet\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4 RestNet\"></a>4 RestNet</h2><p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/Fr78uMsjGaOqA2S.png\"></p>\n<p>两种残差块</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/Z4VHLtBUg93f5GT.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/rEjFCJP4uILKYlo.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/CMDERm4U2vBysTz.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/mcwfbsKGh6jRpxW.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/h9LixO8wBUXJozb.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"5-MobileNet\"><a href=\"#5-MobileNet\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5 MobileNet\"></a>5 MobileNet</h2><h3 id=\"5-1-MobileNet-V1\"><a href=\"#5-1-MobileNet-V1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5.1 MobileNet V1\"></a>5.1 MobileNet V1</h3><p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/yGHa8ACMZVhJ2xn.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/V9anObAtLQ4lhsU.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/zmAwdDPi6nuYhGZ.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/g1Rawx3m48yXjdQ.png\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"5-2-MobileNet-V2\"><a href=\"#5-2-MobileNet-V2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5.2 MobileNet V2\"></a>5.2 MobileNet V2</h3><p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/bGuwxOJPI3qpKN9.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/aiMUoZCcSuHQlnR.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/sG3n6jDYAEB9hax.png\"></p>\n<p>这个n表示我们使用多少个该倒残差结构，这个图上s仅仅是针对的<strong>第一个</strong>倒残差结构的<strong>第一层</strong>，如果有两个倒残差结构，</p>\n<p>那么第二个倒残差结构的第一层就是1，和图上无关。</p>\n<p>这个扩展因子t指的是倒残差结构的第一层1 * 1卷积的输出channel是输入channel的多少倍，也就是一共有t * k个1 * 1 的卷积核。具体可以看上面一张图。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/YOXkvGzIQ7jRm3b.png\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"5-3-MobileNet-V3\"><a href=\"#5-3-MobileNet-V3\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5.3 MobileNet V3\"></a>5.3 MobileNet V3</h3><p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/DrTMbqkduZB83Xj.png\"></p>\n<p>创新1：更新Block</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/drKbAzp1g5qNJ6h.png\"></p>\n<p>SE模块 ：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/hLVgcxXSInWTjBl.png\"></p>\n<p>更新的激活函数：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/2jQNoVRlBb8nKsq.png\"></p>\n<p>创新2：重新设计耗时层结构</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/bYMJBt2VzuIcFwW.png\"></p>\n<p><strong>网络设计：</strong></p>\n<p><strong>exp_size</strong>：经过1 * 1卷积升到多少维度</p>\n<p><strong>这个注意点</strong>：本来1 * 1的卷积我们是希望它起到升维的作用的，但是在图上会发现这一层的eexp_size和输入的channel</p>\n<p>是一样大小的，这也就是说在这一层其实并没有用到1 * 1卷积。论文中这里没有说，留意下即可。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/25/1PNvS47ZFEGkQJj.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"6-ShuffleNet\"><a href=\"#6-ShuffleNet\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6 ShuffleNet\"></a>6 ShuffleNet</h2><h3 id=\"6-1-ShuffleNet-V1\"><a href=\"#6-1-ShuffleNet-V1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6.1 ShuffleNet V1\"></a>6.1 ShuffleNet V1</h3><p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/27/pjKzenV6HWhsDJa.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/27/yr5WNcmZ73LIfHl.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/27/5Hn8c3XjRiLMgSV.png\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"6-2-ShuffleNet-V2\"><a href=\"#6-2-ShuffleNet-V2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6.2 ShuffleNet V2\"></a>6.2 ShuffleNet V2</h3><p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/27/1AB47r23vXu6QwL.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/27/Rved5ao7XtFznYc.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/27/SeAyW2569ZFn147.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/27/9BSpIKsDbNaZ3kh.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/27/mj6bQuWIMTD1Jzq.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/27/bqDysaozTtGkL5V.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"7-EfficientNet\"><a href=\"#7-EfficientNet\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"7 EfficientNet\"></a>7 EfficientNet</h2><p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/28/vJnhOGQ8fqVD1jT.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/28/Eyvawri7WNmKzbZ.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/28/fld3zboDTV6jCx2.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/28/ZW4VxTeqgpHYsXS.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/28/Nv7Xf9SgmZzsTOx.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"8-FPN\"><a href=\"#8-FPN\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"8 FPN\"></a>8 FPN</h2><p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/05/13/fR943MVZLtsgBHX.png\"></p>\n<p>网络结构：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/05/13/qBu3Xc8amyzJFKC.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/05/13/qcJ5NUenZTDQCSx.png\"></p>\n","text":"1 AlexNet 2 VGG 3 GooleNet 4 RestNet 两种残差块 5 MobileNet5.1 MobileNet V1 5.2 Mobil...","permalink":"/post/Image_Classfication","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":565,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-AlexNet\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1 AlexN